TITLE: Basic HMR Implementation Example
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to implement basic hot module replacement using both module.hot and import.meta.webpackHot approaches
SOURCE: https://github.com/web-infra-dev/rspack/blob/main/website/docs/en/api/runtime-api/hmr.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
if (module.hot) {
  module.hot.accept('./library.js', function () {
    // Do something with the updated library module...
  });
}

// or
if (import.meta.webpackHot) {
  import.meta.webpackHot.accept('./library.js', function () {
    // Do something with the updated library module…
  });
}
```

