TITLE: Removing an Asset with processAssets Hook in Rspack
DESCRIPTION: Example demonstrating how to delete an unwanted asset during the PROCESS_ASSETS_STAGE_OPTIMIZE stage of the compilation process using the processAssets hook.
SOURCE: https://github.com/web-infra-dev/rspack/blob/main/website/docs/en/api/plugin-api/compilation-hooks.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_14

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
compiler.hooks.thisCompilation.tap('MyPlugin', compilation => {
  const { Compilation } = compiler.webpack;
  compilation.hooks.processAssets.tap(
    {
      name: 'MyPlugin',
      stage: Compilation.PROCESS_ASSETS_STAGE_OPTIMIZE,
    },
    assets => {
      const assetName = 'unwanted-script.js';
      if (assets[assetName]) {
        compilation.deleteAsset(assetName);
      }
    },
  );
});
```

