TITLE: Hot Update Test Example
DESCRIPTION: This JavaScript snippet demonstrates a unit test case for hot updates in a Rspack project. It tests if a module correctly updates when the underlying file changes, using the NEXT method to control update timing.
SOURCE: https://github.com/web-infra-dev/rspack/blob/main/website/docs/en/contribute/development/testing-rspack.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: js
