TITLE: Loading Async Chunks with Common Modules in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Example showing two different methods of async chunk loading that share common modules 'a' and 'b'. The first chunk loads modules a, b, c using array syntax, while the second uses require.ensure to load modules a, b, d. Rspack will automatically optimize these by extracting the common modules (a, b) into a separate chunk.
