TITLE: Implementing Chat Functionality in a Shared Worker
DESCRIPTION: This Shared Worker script manages chat history and connects multiple clients. It handles message addition and history retrieval, demonstrating the use of Shared Workers for maintaining shared state across multiple tabs or windows.
SOURCE: https://github.com/web-infra-dev/rspack/blob/main/tests/webpack-examples/worker/README.md#2025-04-21_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import { history, add } from "./chat-module";

onconnect = function (e) {
	for (const port of e.ports) {
		port.onmessage = event => {
			const msg = event.data;
			switch (msg.type) {
				case "message":
					add(msg.content, msg.from);
				// fallthrough
				case "history":
					port.postMessage({
						type: "history",
						history
					});
					break;
			}
		};
	}
};
```

