DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to configure the `environment` option in the `rspack.config.mjs` file. This option specifies which ES features are supported in the generated runtime code, such as arrow functions, async functions, and template literals. Each feature can be enabled or disabled using a boolean value.
