TITLE: Implementing Lazy Compilation Middleware in Rspack
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to integrate the new Express-style lazy compilation middleware into a custom development server setup. This improves upon the previous separate server approach.
SOURCE: https://github.com/web-infra-dev/rspack/blob/main/website/docs/en/blog/announcing-1-3.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import { rspack } from '@rspack/core';
import config from './rspack.config.mjs';
import DevServer from 'webpack-dev-server';

const compiler = rspack(config);
const middleware = rspack.experiments.lazyCompilationMiddleware(
  compiler,
  config.experiments.lazyCompilation,
);

const server = new DevServer(
  {
    setupMiddlewares(other) {
      return [middleware, ...other];
    },
  },
  compiler,
);
```

