TITLE: Filtering Dynamic Imports with webpack Include/Exclude Patterns
DESCRIPTION: This function demonstrates how to use webpack's contextModule to filter dynamic imports. It uses webpackInclude and webpackExclude inline comments to control which files are bundled - including only .js files while excluding any files ending with .noimport.js.
