TITLE: Conditional HMR Accepting Example
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates conditional accepting of dependencies with invalidation logic
SOURCE: https://github.com/web-infra-dev/rspack/blob/main/website/docs/en/api/runtime-api/hmr.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import { x, y } from './dep';
import { processX, processY } from 'anotherDep';

const oldY = y;

processX(x);
export default processY(y);

module.hot.accept('./dep', () => {
  if (y !== oldY) {
    // This can't be handled, bubble to parent
    module.hot.invalidate();
    return;
  }
  // This can be handled
  processX(x);
});
```

