TITLE: Extract Style Loader Implementation
DESCRIPTION: A loader that extracts CSS styles from JavaScript files and creates a new import with matchResource that will be processed by CSS rules. It uses regex to find style definitions and transforms them into imports.
SOURCE: https://github.com/web-infra-dev/rspack/blob/main/website/docs/en/api/loader-api/inline-match-resource.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const getStylesLoader = require.resolve('./getStyles');

module.exports = function (source) {
  if (STYLES_REGEXP.test(source)) {
    source = source.replace(STYLES_REGEXP, '');
    return `import ${JSON.stringify(
      this.utils.contextify(
        this.context || this.rootContext,
        `${this.resource}.css!=!${getStylesLoader}!${this.remainingRequest}`,
      ),
    )};${source}`;
  }
  return source;
};
```

