TITLE: Increment Module Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Module providing increment-related functions using math module dependency.
SOURCE: https://github.com/web-infra-dev/rspack/blob/main/tests/webpack-examples/cjs-tree-shaking/README.md#2025-04-21_snippet_1

