TITLE: Defining WatchFileSystem Type for File System Watching in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This type definition outlines the structure of a file system watcher. It includes a watch function that takes files, directories, and options as input, and provides callbacks for changes. The returned object offers methods to control and retrieve information about the watching process.
