TITLE: Type Definitions for DllReferencePlugin Options in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Comprehensive TypeScript type definitions for the DllReferencePlugin options, including content structure, manifest options, source types, and main plugin configuration options.
SOURCE: https://github.com/web-infra-dev/rspack/blob/main/website/docs/en/plugins/webpack/dll-reference-plugin.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_0

