TITLE: Configuring SWC Loader with React and Emotion in Rspack 0.4
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to configure the builtin SWC loader for JSX files with React and Emotion support in Rspack 0.4. It includes settings for the JavaScript compiler (jsc) and Rspack experiments.
SOURCE: https://github.com/web-infra-dev/rspack/blob/main/website/docs/en/blog/announcing-0-4.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
export default {
  module: {
    rules: [
      {
        test: /\.jsx$/,
        loader: 'builtin:swc-loader',
        options: {
          jsc: {
            parser: {
              syntax: 'ecmascript',
              jsx: true,
            },
            transform: {
              react: {
                runtime: 'automatic',
              },
            },
          },
          rspackExperiments: {
            emotion: true, // The same as `builtins`
          },
        },
        type: 'javascript/auto',
      },
    ],
  },
  experiments: {
    rspackFuture: {
      disableTransformByDefault: true,
    },
  },
};
```

