TITLE: Configuring svelte-loader in Rspack
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet shows the Rspack configuration for integrating Svelte. It sets up proper module resolution with alias for Svelte, configures appropriate file extensions and main fields, and adds svelte-loader with development and production options.
SOURCE: https://github.com/web-infra-dev/rspack/blob/main/website/docs/en/guide/tech/svelte.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: js
CODE:
