TITLE: Polyfill Injection with Rspack SWC Loader
DESCRIPTION: This snippet illustrates how to configure SWC to inject polyfills for APIs using `core-js`. The `env.mode` is set to `usage` to enable polyfill injection based on usage.  `env.coreJs` specifies the version of `core-js` to use. The configuration also includes `isModule: 'unknown'` for handling non-ES modules and excludes `core-js` from SWC compilation.
