TITLE: Mathematical Function Exports
DESCRIPTION: Module exporting mathematical utility functions including add, multiply and list. Demonstrates ES6 named exports with function implementations.
SOURCE: https://github.com/web-infra-dev/rspack/blob/main/tests/webpack-examples/harmony-unused/README.md#2025-04-21_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
export function add() {
	var sum = 0, i = 0, args = arguments, l = args.length;
	while (i < l) {
		sum += args[i++];
	}
	return sum;
}

export function multiply() {
	var product = 1, i = 0, args = arguments, l = args.length;
	while (i < l) {
		product *= args[i++];
	}
	return product;
}

export function list() {
	return Array.from(arguments);
}
```

