TITLE: Defining ChunkGroup Type Structure in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet defines the structure of a ChunkGroup type in TypeScript. It includes properties for name, index, chunks, and origins, as well as methods for checking if it's initial, getting files, and getting parent chunk groups.
