TITLE: Configuring SWC Loader for JSX/TSX Support in Rspack
DESCRIPTION: This configuration enables JSX support in Rspack using the built-in SWC loader. It includes React-specific transformation options for JSX syntax.
SOURCE: https://github.com/web-infra-dev/rspack/blob/main/website/docs/en/guide/tech/typescript.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: js
CODE:
```
export default {
  module: {
    rules: [
      {
        test: /\.jsx$/,
        use: {
          loader: 'builtin:swc-loader',
          options: {
            jsc: {
              parser: {
                syntax: 'ecmascript',
                jsx: true,
              },
              transform: {
                react: {
                  pragma: 'React.createElement',
                  pragmaFrag: 'React.Fragment',
                  throwIfNamespace: true,
                  development: false,
                  useBuiltins: false,
                },
              },
            },
          },
        },
        type: 'javascript/auto',
      },
    ],
  },
};
```

