DESCRIPTION: This snippet introduces an asynchronous function for chunk loading, managing deferred chunk execution. It processes a queue of deferred chunks and executes them based on certain priorities.
SOURCE: https://github.com/web-infra-dev/rspack/blob/main/tests/webpack-examples/code-splitting-depend-on-advanced/README.md#2025-04-21_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
