TITLE: Moving Async Script Tags with alterAssetTagGroups Hook in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Example of using the alterAssetTagGroups hook to move async script tags from body to head. This demonstrates how to adjust the insertion position of tags.
SOURCE: https://github.com/web-infra-dev/rspack/blob/main/website/docs/en/plugins/rspack/html-rspack-plugin.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_27

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const MoveTagsPlugin = {
  apply(compiler) {
    compiler.hooks.compilation.tap('MoveTagsPlugin', compilation => {
      HtmlWebpackPlugin.getCompilationHooks(
        compilation,
      ).alterAssetTagGroups.tapPromise('MoveTagsPlugin', async data => {
        data.headTags.push(data.headTags.bodyTags.filter(i => i.async));
        data.bodyTags = data.bodyTags.filter(i => !i.async);
      });
    });
  },
};

export default {
  //...
  plugins: [
    new HtmlRspackPlugin({
      inject: 'body',
    }),
    AllHeadTagsPlugin,
  ],
};
```

