TITLE: Node.js Process Polyfill for Browsers
DESCRIPTION: A comprehensive polyfill implementing the Node.js process object for browser environments. Includes implementations for nextTick, environment variables, and various process methods with special handling for Internet Explorer edge cases.
SOURCE: https://github.com/web-infra-dev/rspack/blob/main/packages/rspack-test-tools/tests/builtinCases/plugin-javascript/provide/__snapshots__/output.snap.txt#2025-04-21_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
