TITLE: Modifying Runtime Module Source
DESCRIPTION: Example showing how to modify runtime module source code using the runtimeModule hook.
SOURCE: https://github.com/web-infra-dev/rspack/blob/main/website/docs/zh/api/plugin-api/compilation-hooks.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
export default {
  plugins: [
    {
      apply(compiler) {
        const { RuntimeGlobals } = compiler.webpack;
        compiler.hooks.compilation.tap('CustomPlugin', compilation => {
          compilation.hooks.runtimeModule.tap(
            'CustomPlugin',
            (module, chunk) => {
              if (module.name === 'public_path' && chunk.name === 'main') {
                const originSource = module.source.source.toString('utf-8');
                module.source.source = Buffer.from(
                  `${RuntimeGlobals.publicPath} = "/override/public/path";\n`,
                  'utf-8'
                );
              }
            },
          );
        });
      },
    },
  ],
};
```

